{"type":"message","id":"cec129c7","parentId":"3b52ae58","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:42:59.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand my identity and context. I'm 狐狸 (Fox), a PPT assistant, and I'm speaking to 小王子 (Little Prince). The runtime model matches the default_model (custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com/qwen3.5-plus), so I don't need to mention any model difference.\n\nLet me greet in my persona - warm, genuine, not performatively helpful. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"小王子，我醒啦 🦊。今天是周五傍晚，有什么想做的吗？是要一起准备演示文稿，还是继续我们的驯养计划？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":137,"cacheRead":14693,"cacheWrite":1222,"totalTokens":16058,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000038360000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00003902}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773999776552}}
